author: dlr
msg: On the ra-replay-dev branch: Activate basic, rough command-line tests
for SVNSync.  The implementation of these tests could use some
(build_repos): A helper function similar to Sandbox.build() which
only sets up -- and cleans up -- an empty repository, avoiding
loading it with the Greek tree.
(run_and_verify_load): A helper function which runs 'svnadmin load'
(run_test): A helper function which provides the majority of the
logic for all SVNSync tests.  It loads a dump file, syncs
run_test() function with the appropriate dump file name.
(run_svnsync): A companion function for the svnsync_binary variable,
which runs svnsync with the provided argument list, and returns
stdout and stderr as a list of lines.
